  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VEIL OF MIST AND RAIN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CRYSTALS BLOOM IN SILVER LIGHT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROFITS RISE LIKE STARS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sent to a <strong>foggy planet</strong> as a contractor, your only way out is to <strong>gather enough money</strong> for the fly back home. Beware <strong>the rain</strong> that always seems to <strong>follow you</strong> and <strong>listen</strong> for its messages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smash</strong> crystals, <strong>dodge</strong> rain, make <strong>money</strong>, <strong>upgrade</strong> your equipment, <strong>keep going</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When will you go <strong>back home</strong>?<br><br><strong>I made this by myself in around a month so don't expect a very long game, the playtime is around a couple of hours!</strong><br><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><strong>Left Click:</strong> Hammer<br><strong>Right Click:</strong> Active Items<br><strong>Shift:</strong> Sprint<br><strong>Tab:</strong> Inventory<br><strong>Escape:</strong> Menu</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VEIL OF MIST AND RAIN</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CRYSTALS BLOOM IN SILVER LIGHT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROFITS RISE LIKE STARS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sent to a <strong>foggy planet</strong> as a contractor, your only way out is to <strong>gather enough money</strong> for the fly back home. Beware <strong>the rain</strong> that always seems to <strong>follow you</strong> and <strong>listen</strong> for its messages.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Smash</strong> crystals, <strong>dodge</strong> rain, make <strong>money</strong>, <strong>upgrade</strong> your equipment, <strong>keep going</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When will you go <strong>back home</strong>?<br><br><strong>I made this by myself in around a month so don't expect a very long game, the playtime is around a couple of hours!</strong><br><br><strong>Controls</strong><br><strong>Left Click:</strong> Hammer<br><strong>Right Click:</strong> Active Items<br><strong>Shift:</strong> Sprint<br><strong>Tab:</strong> Inventory<br><strong>Escape:</strong> Menu</p>",
